snippet: Joshua Houston struck out five in five innings, and Jackie Robinson West of Chicago beat Pearland, Tex., 6-1, in an elimination game on Tuesday in the Little League World Series.
abstract: Joshua Houston strikes out five in five innings, and Jackie Robinson West of Chicago beats Pearland, Tex, 6-1, in elimination game in the Little League World Series in South Williamsport, Pa; other Little League World Series baseball news noted.
